%F A228787 s(17) = 2*sin(Pi/17) = 2*A241243.
%F A228787 Equals sqrt(34-2*sqrt(17)-2*sqrt(34-2*sqrt(17))-4*sqrt(17+3*sqrt(17)-sqrt(34-2*sqrt(17))-2*sqrt(34+2*sqrt(17))))/4. - _Stanislav Sykora_, May 02 2016
